# Edooka project conventions

## Stack
- Next.js App Router, TypeScript strict, Tailwind v4
- Drizzle ORM with PostgreSQL (Supabase)
- @react-pdf/renderer for PDFs
- Resend for email
- Cashfree for payments

## Security
- Never expose service role key to client components
- Verify all webhook signatures server-side
- Keep payment logic only in API routes or server actions

## Business rules
- Pass threshold is 50% (9 out of 18)
- Pass screen: show "You qualified", no percentage
- Fail screen: show raw count only, no percentage
- Retry lock: 24 hours on failed attempts
